  "sprint_completed": "v8.26",
  "_v544_dispatch_note": "SPA-V544 (MP-620): ChainExposureReport — advisory/read-only агрегация экспозиции портфеля по БЛОКЧЕЙНАМ (ethereum/arbitrum/base/optimism/polygon/UNKNOWN). HHI chain-концентрация, policy chain-concentration cap (ethereum<=70% AUM, MP-387), chain-weighted APY, флаг L2-экспозиции, Telegram-сводка. Третий срез того же источника data/yield_attribution_tracker.json (после stablecoin_exposure_report и tier_exposure_report). Pure stdlib, atomic writes (tmp+os.replace), ring-buffer 30, fail-safe загрузка, CLI --check/--run/--data-dir, всегда exit(0). 183 tests green. Текущий снапшот: ethereum 100% > 70% cap → policy BREACH, HHI=1.000 CONCENTRATED (корректный флаг chain-концентрации).",
  "_v412_dispatch_note": "SPA-V412 (MP-113): exit_latency_hours declared on all 6 adapters (Aave/Compound/Morpho/Euler 0h instant, Yearn 1h, Maple 336h queue), added as optional additive field on YieldInfo, plus read-only spa_core/adapters/exit_latency_policy.py (check_exit_latency_policy: illiquid>72h share <=25%; kill_switch_exit_order: liquid-first ADVISORY ordering only, no execution). +17 tests, 146 adapter tests green (pytest). Strictly read-only/additive; execution/risk/feed_health untouched (SPA-BL-011).",
  "_v413_dispatch_note": "SPA-V413 (MP-209-prep): read-only/advisory capacity analytics. New spa_core/paper_trading/capacity_analytics.py (stdlib-only, pure-function core + thin file loader, mirror of exit_latency_policy.py): per-pool max_position_usd = min(TVL*MAX_TVL_SHARE=2%, daily_exit_volume*MAX_DAILY_VOLUME_SHARE=10%; daily volume proxied as TVL*DAILY_LIQUIDITY_FRACTION=10% when no volume feed, flagged volume_source=proxy_from_tvl); capacity_adjusted_apy = base_apy*(1 - slippage_penalty), penalty linear in utilization up to MAX_SLIPPAGE_PENALTY=30% at full capacity; portfolio scalability ceiling max_aum = min_i(max_position_i / weight_i); grade A-D / verdict (A>=$50M, B>=$10M, C>=$1M, D<$1M). Inputs: adapter_orchestrator_status.json + target_allocation.json. Atomic write data/capacity_analytics.json with execution_mode=read_only_simulation + assumptions block. +31 unit tests green; regression test_exit_latency+test_adapter_orchestrator 46/46 green; py_compile clean; no stray tmp; no forbidden imports (web3/requests/execution/risk/feed_health/anthropic). Real-data verdict: max_aum ~$20.1K, grade D, verdict capacity_constrained -- bottleneck morpho_blue (TVL ~$403K at 20% weight). STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): computes advisory numbers only, enforcement of per-cap stays with deterministic risk agent. Push attempted via push_to_github.py (Keychain GITHUB_PAT_SPA).",
  "_v414_dispatch_note": "SPA-V414 (MP-007): dashboard live-data only. loadDashboard now feeds renderDashboard via buildLiveStatus()/mapOrchToProtocols() built from adapter_orchestrator_status.json + current_positions.json + paper_trading_status.json + equity_curve_daily.json; demo snapshot reads (status.json, protocols.json, strategy_state.json, strategy_v2.json, backtest_results.json, alerts.json, latest_report.json, optimization_recommendations.json, decision_log.json, portfolio_status.json) removed; widgets without live feed show honest 'no data'. Staleness banner when freshest key source >24h (red >72h); real-track day counter computed in JS from REAL_TRACK_START=2026-06-10. VaR shows '—' while risk_metrics stale (MP-012). node --check syntax-clean; +9 static tests green (test_dashboard_live_data.py); regression 76/78 (2 pre-existing fails in test_dashboard_adapter_sync: SPA-V334 contract pins 5 adapters vs 7 in data/adapter_status.json since 2026-05-31 — drift unrelated to this sprint, follow-up flagged). Unblocks MP-110 (investor view). STRICTLY READ-ONLY: HTML/JS + tests only; execution/risk/wallet/feed-health untouched (SPA-BL-011). || SPA-V414 (MP-011+MP-012): Compound V3 полностью в runtime — tier T1 синхронизирован везде (класс TIER=\"T1\"/T1_CAP=0.40 как у Aave, fetch(), YieldInfo, оба ADAPTER_REGISTRY; ровно 2 T1-якоря), production-снимок: compound_v3 ok, live APY 3.18%, TVL $48.6M. risk_scores.json теперь регенерируется каждым daily-циклом ДО аллокации (cycle_runner шаг 0b, fail-safe: исключение → WARNING, цикл живёт на старом снимке; запись атомарная tmp+os.replace в scoring_engine.export). Живой прогон: ts 2026-06-10T18:19Z (stale с 2026-05-27 устранён), compound-v3 = B. Тесты: 12 новых (test_risk_scores_regen.py) + обновлён test_compound_v3 (31); регрессия 290/290 green по 11 сьютам (orchestrator 29, compound_v3 31, risk_adjusted_alloc 24, allocator 19, risk_policy_gate 15, cycle_runner 20, golive 17, scoring_engine 92, aave 18, cash_drag 13, regen 12). STRICTLY READ-ONLY: execution/feed_health/детерминированные агенты не тронуты.",
  "_v415_dispatch_note": "SPA-V415 (MP-101): gap-monitor трека — CRITICAL-алерт + auto-recovery. check_gaps() при gap пишет дедуплицированный critical-алерт (source=gap_monitor, type=cycle_gap) в risk_alerts.json, не затирая чужие алерты; attempt_recovery() под file-lock запускает штатный run_cycle() (paper only, read-only simulation), идемпотентно (1 попытка/UTC-день), честная фиксация failure (cycle_ran_but_gap_persists / exception). CLI: python3 -m spa_core.paper_trading.gap_monitor --recover. STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): execution/risk/wallet не тронуты, сетевых вызовов в тестах нет.",
  "_v416_dispatch_note": "SPA-V416 (MP-309): CI lint enforcing the project constitution in code — LLM SDK imports are FORBIDDEN in the deterministic L2/L3 domains (spa_core/risk, spa_core/execution, spa_core/allocator). New spa_core/ci/llm_forbidden_lint.py: pure-stdlib AST scanner (no network, never imports the SDKs it hunts), dotted-prefix matching for anthropic/google.generativeai/openai/langchain/litellm, JSON report data/llm_forbidden_lint.json written atomically, CLI exit codes 0/1/2 (ok/violations/no_dirs), SyntaxError files bucketed as parse_errors instead of crashing CI. 23 unittest cases incl. the live enforcement test 'real repo is clean' (live run: status=ok, 3 dirs, 27 files, 0 violations). Also fixed the 2 pre-existing red tests in test_dashboard_adapter_sync.py (pytest->unittest, SPA-V334 contract updated from 5 to 7 adapters, expected keys now derived from the _ADAPTER_SPECS registry via read-only AST). Kanban hygiene: MP-108 (status=done) moved backlog->done. Sprint selection: v4.15 ends in 5 so an architect review was required; the stock architect.py was blocked by the sandbox (no anthropic module, no ANTHROPIC_API_KEY) -> manual architect review fallback performed by the LLM orchestrator (backlog had no ready code tasks; MP-309 taken from features). STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): the lint only READS risk/execution/allocator source; nothing in those domains was modified.",
  "_v417_dispatch_note": "SPA-V417 (MP-204): Adapter SDK v1 — declarative YAML/JSON adapters. New additive package spa_core/adapter_sdk/ (contract.py / manifest.py / declarative_adapter.py / registry.py / manifests/): formal ProtocolAdapter contract (fetch_pools->list[PoolInfo] compatible with adapter_orchestrator_status.json field shapes, exit_latency dict in exit_latency_policy.py style with 72h illiquid threshold, health ok/degraded/error with last_fetch_ts/source); manifest schema (name, defillama_protocol_id, chains/symbols, tier+cap defaults T1 .40/T2 .20/T3 .10, exit_latency profile, quality gates min_tvl_usd/stable_only/max_apy_pct) validated into a single ValidationError carrying the FULL problems list (no stacktraces); PyYAML optional — .json manifests and JSON-compatible .yaml bodies load without it; DeclarativeAdapter reuses the existing DeFiLlamaFeed (no duplicated HTTP), feed loss/exceptions degrade honestly to fetch_pools=[] + health=error (never raises, never mocks); registry discovers manifests/*.yaml|*.yml|*.json, broken manifests are quarantined per-file without killing the registry, CLI exit 0/1/2 (ok/invalid manifests/empty dir), atomic data/adapter_sdk_status.json (tmp+os.replace), --no-write/--no-fetch (offline: feed disabled, zero egress). 3 demo manifests for protocols NOT among the file adapters: spark (T2, cap .20), fluid-lending (T2, cap .15), curve-dex 3pool (T3, cap .10) with conservative quality gates. Tests: 47 new (test_adapter_sdk.py, unittest, no network — fake/dead/raising feeds injected, CLI via subprocess --no-fetch); regression 100/100 (adapter_orchestrator+exit_latency+capacity_analytics+llm_forbidden_lint); llm_forbidden_lint exit 0; py_compile clean; live registry run in sandbox: 3/3 manifests valid, health=error (egress to yields.llama.fi blocked — honest degradation), exit 0, no stray *.tmp. STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): risk/execution/allocator/wallet/feed-health/cycle_runner/existing adapters untouched; push is done by the orchestrator.",
  "_v418_dispatch_note": "SPA-V418 (2026-06-11): MP-205 Candidate-tier автодискавери поверх Adapter SDK v1 (MP-204, v4.17). discovery.py сканирует DeFiLlama по quality-gates (TVL>=$5M, age>=180d/age_unknown, stable-only, APY<=30%, минус уже покрытые протоколы) в ADVISORY-реестр data/candidate_registry.json — whitelist только через ADR/человека; 44 теста зелёные, живой прогон в песочнице честно degraded до status=error (egress к yields.llama.fi заблокирован).",
  "_v419_dispatch_note": "SPA-V419 (2026-06-11): MP-206 инкремент 1 — «20+ адаптеров через SDK», батч 2 из 9 новых декларативных манифестов в spa_core/adapter_sdk/manifests/ (было 3 → стало 12; цель 20+, MP-206 остаётся в features). Состав по карточке MP-206 (Convex, Gearbox passive, Ethena capped, Across LP + стабильные AMM/lending): ethena_susde (ethena-usde, SUSDE, T3 cap 0.05 «ось peg», exit 168h illiquid), gearbox (T3, USDC/USDT, instant), across (T3, USDC/USDT, 1h), stargate (T3, USDC/USDT, 1h), velodrome_stable (velodrome-v2, Optimism, USDC-SUSD, T3), convex_3pool (convex-finance, DAI-USDC-USDT, T3), balancer_stable (balancer-v2, GHO-USDC-USDT, T3), aerodrome_stable (aerodrome-v1, Base, DOLA-USDC, T3), venus (venus-core-pool, BSC, USDT/USDC, T3). Все — candidate-tier гейты: min_tvl_usd>=5M, stable_only=true (каждая нога из STABLE_SYMBOLS), max_apy_pct<=30; exit_latency объявлен явно у всех; sky/sUSDS пропущен (есть execution/adapters/sky_susds_adapter.py), дублей с файловыми адаптерами (aave-v3/compound-v3/morpho-blue/euler-v2/maple/yearn-finance/pendle) и батчем 1 (spark/fluid-lending/curve-dex) нет — slugs уникальны, substring-матчинг проверен в обе стороны. Тесты: spa_core/tests/test_manifests_batch2.py — 25 новых unittest-кейсов 25/25 OK (без сети, DeadFeed); регрессия test_adapter_sdk+test_discovery+test_llm_forbidden_lint 114/114 OK; llm_forbidden_lint exit 0; py_compile чисто; registry --no-fetch: manifests=12 valid=12 invalid=0 exit 0, data/adapter_sdk_status.json перезаписан (offline, честный health=error). STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): risk/execution/allocator/cycle_runner/defillama_feed/существующие адаптеры/push_to_github.py не тронуты; пуш делает оркестратор.",
  "_v420_dispatch_note": "SPA-V420 (2026-06-11): MP-206 инкремент 2 (финальный) — «20+ адаптеров через SDK», батч 3 из 9 новых декларативных манифестов в spa_core/adapter_sdk/manifests/ (было 12 → стало 21; цель 20+ достигнута, ЭПИК ЗАКРЫТ). Состав по карточке MP-206 (crvUSD, Frax, Notional + консервативные stable-lending): crvusd_llamalend (curve-llamalend, CRVUSD, T3 cap 0.05 «ось peg», exit 1h liquid), fraxlend (FRAX, T3 cap 0.05 «ось peg», 1h), notional_v3 (notional-v3, USDC, T3 0.10, 24h liquid), silo (silo-v2, Arbitrum, USDC, T3 0.10, 1h), moonwell (Base, USDC, T3 0.10, instant), dolomite (Arbitrum, USDC, T3 0.10, instant), benqi (benqi-lending, Avalanche, USDC/USDT, T3 0.10, instant), clearpool (clearpool-lending, USDC, T3 cap 0.05 — uncollateralized credit, 24h), ipor (USDC, T3 cap 0.05, 24h). Все — candidate-tier гейты: min_tvl_usd>=5M, stable_only=true (CRVUSD/FRAX уже в STABLE_SYMBOLS — множество НЕ менялось), max_apy_pct<=30 (25 у credit); тиры только T3; exit_latency объявлен явно у всех, profile==bucket; дублей с файловыми адаптерами (aave-v3/compound-v3/morpho-blue/euler-v2/maple/yearn-finance/pendle/sky-susds) и батчами 1-2 нет — substring в обе стороны. Тесты: spa_core/tests/test_manifests_batch3.py — 27 unittest-кейсов 27/27 OK (без сети, DeadFeed); регрессия test_adapter_sdk+test_discovery+test_manifests_batch2+test_llm_forbidden_lint 139/139 OK; llm_forbidden_lint exit 0; registry --no-fetch: manifests=21 valid=21 invalid=0 exit 0, data/adapter_sdk_status.json перезаписан (offline, честный health=error), хвостовых *.tmp нет. STRICTLY READ-ONLY (SPA-BL-011): risk/execution/allocator/cycle_runner/defillama_feed/существующие адаптеры и манифесты/push_to_github.py не тронуты; пуш делает оркестратор.",
