      "description": "WeeklySummaryReport: агрегирует последние 7 дней из data/daily_ops_report.json (ring-buffer). Dataclasses: WeeklyStats (metric_name, values, avg, min, max, trend: RISING/FALLING/STABLE — last > first+0.1→RISING, last < first-0.1→FALLING, иначе STABLE), WeeklySummaryReportData (generated_at, week_start, week_end, days_covered, apy_stats, operational_days, degraded_days, critical_days, best_day_apy, worst_day_apy, top_chain_this_week, top_chain_apy, weekly_verdict, summary_line). Helpers: _safe_float, _parse_timestamp (Z→+00:00, fromisoformat), _compute_trend, _trend_arrow. WeeklySummaryReport(data_path): load_daily_history()→list[dict] (daily_ops_report.json history, фильтр non-dict, graceful на missing); get_last_7_days(history)→sort ascending by generated_at, tail 7; compute_weekly_stats(values, name)→WeeklyStats; _determine_verdict(avg_apy, op_days): EXCELLENT(>6%+≥5op)/GOOD(>5% OR ≥4op)/FAIR(>4%)/POOR; _extract_top_chain→(chain, avg_apy); generate_report()→WeeklySummaryReportData (0 дней→POOR/нули); save_report()→атомарный tmp+os.replace, ring-buffer 12 в data/weekly_summary.json; format_telegram_message()≤1500 chars (📅 header, verdict emoji, APY avg/min/max/trend, best/worst day, top chain, degraded/critical, trend label); to_dict()→JSON-serializable. CLI: --check/--run/--data-dir. Pure stdlib, 97 tests green.",
