  "_v648_dispatch_note": "v6.48: MP-821 ProtocolIncentiveDecayMonitor (87 tests, ACTIVE..EXHAUSTED exit signal, budget decay APY projection, HOLD..EXIT_NOW recommendation) + MP-822 AutoCompounderAnalyzer (80 tests, vault EAR vs manual gas break-even, USE/SKIP recommendation, ring-buffer logs, atomic writes, stdlib only) — 167 tests green",
