  "_v655_reconcile_note": "RACE: parallel run claimed v6.55/MP-835 (CorrelationRiskAnalyzer) + MP-836 (GovernanceHealthScorer), wrote push_v655.sh at 19:11 but had not committed KANBAN/sprint_log. This orchestrator re-tagged its own work to v6.56/MP-837/MP-838 (unique filenames sortino_ratio_calculator.py + lending_pool_utilization_analyzer.py — no rename needed) and reconciled both sets into done.",
  "_v656_reconcile_note": "RACE (parallel run B): claimed MP-837 DeFiGasOptimizationAdvisor + MP-838 ProtocolSecurityAuditTracker, wrote push_v656.sh ~19:19. This orchestrator inadvertently overwrote push_v656.sh and has restored it (206 tests green); both modules+tests verified on disk and reconciled into done.",
  "_v657_dispatch_note": "v6.57: MP-839 SortinoRatioCalculator (119 tests, downside semi-deviation, annualized Sortino vs Sharpe, NO_DOWNSIDE/NEGATIVE_RETURN/HIGH_DOWNSIDE_VOL flags, A-F) + MP-840 LendingPoolUtilizationAnalyzer (118 tests, kinked borrow/supply rate model, UNDERUTILIZED..CRITICAL regime, ILLIQUID/OVER_KINK/RATE_SPIKE_RISK flags). 237 tests green. Re-tagged from v6.55->v6.56->v6.57 / MP-835->837->839 due to 3-way race with parallel runs A(v655) and B(v656). Push: bash scripts/push_v657.sh",
