  "_v664_dispatch_note": "SPA-V664: two advisory analytics modules — MP-851 APYPersistenceScorer (APY temporal stickiness/durability scoring) + MP-852 YieldCurveSteepnessAnalyzer (lock-up term-structure / term-premium analysis). Pure stdlib, read-only/advisory, atomic writes, ring-buffer 100. 250 unittest tests green (132 + 118).",
