  "notes_v675": "v6.75: MP-873 RestakingRiskAnalyzer (88 tests, slashing/AVS/operator-concentration/withdrawal-delay/LRT-depeg weighted score 0-100, LOW..CRITICAL, diversification recs, ring-buffer log) + MP-874 AirdropFarmingValueEstimator (81 tests, expected-airdrop-USD, annualized airdrop yield, opportunity cost vs base APY, net EV, AVOID..HIGHLY_ATTRACTIVE) — 169 tests green, atomic writes, stdlib only",
