  "_v678_dispatch_note": "SPA-V678 (MP-879 DeFiPointsProgramAnalyzer + MP-880 ProtocolFeeRevenueProjector): MP-879 — implied-APY airdrop-probability discounted-value HIGH..SPECULATIVE efficiency-score, 90 tests green; MP-880 — 12m-projection CAGR cycle-adjusted STRONG..AT_RISK growth-trajectory, 109 tests green. 199 tests total. data/points_program_log.json + data/fee_revenue_projection_log.json initialized.",
