  "_v683_dispatch_note": "v6.83: MP-889 DeFiPoolFeeTierOptimizer (IL-adjusted net-score, optimal tier, rationale) + MP-890 ProtocolTVLConcentrationAnalyzer (HHI, systemic risk, DOMINANT..MINOR, by_chain/asset, SINGLE_CHAIN/STABLECOIN_HEAVY flags). 96+94=190 tests green.",
  "_v686_dispatch_note": "SPA-V686: MP-895 DeFiStakingRewardTracker (93 tests, slashing_drag=risk/100*penalty, exit_drag=cost/lockup*365 liquid→0, effective_apy=gross-drag-exit, A+..F grade, NEGATIVE_PREMIUM/HIGH_SLASHING_RISK/LONG_LOCKUP/MANUAL_COMPOUNDING flags, ring-buffer log, atomic writes) + MP-896 ProtocolPartnershipNetworkAnalyzer (80 tests, outbound/inbound degree, HUB..ISOLATED centrality, CRITICAL..LOW dep-risk, tvl_influence_score, network_density, composability_score 0-100, REDUNDANT..NONE resilience, ring-buffer log, atomic writes). 173 tests green. done_count 559->561, sprint_current v6.84->v6.86.",
  "_mp900_milestone": "MP-900 MILESTONE: 900 analytics modules completed! MP-899 DeFiPositionPnLTracker (gross/net PnL, IL drag, fee yield, alpha, EXCEPTIONAL..LOSS labels, HIGH_IL/GAS_HEAVY flags). MP-900 ProtocolSmartMoneyFlowAnalyzer (whale flow divergence, smart money conviction, STRONG_BUY..SELL signals, WHALE_ACCUMULATION/SMART_EXIT flags). 252 tests green (104 MP-899 + 148 MP-900).",
  "notes_v696": "v6.96: MP-916 DeFiProtocolAdoptionTracker (≥80 tests, user_growth_rate, tvl_growth_rate, adoption_velocity_score 0-100, stickiness_score 0-100, network_effect_score 0-100, HYPERGROWTH..DYING labels, 5 flags, ecosystem aggregates, ring-buffer log 100) + MP-917 DeFiYieldSustainabilityRater (≥85 tests, real_yield_ratio, sustainability_score 0-100, emission_dependency, token_drag_pct, HIGHLY_SUSTAINABLE..PONZI_RISK labels, 6 flags, portfolio aggregates, ring-buffer log 100) — 165+ tests green, ring-buffer logs, atomic writes, stdlib only",
  "_v697_dispatch_note": "SPA-V697: MP-918 DeFiGovernanceTokenUtilityScorer (96 tests, cash_flow_yield_pct, utility_score/staking_attractiveness/value_capture_ratio 0-100, HIGH_UTILITY..GOVERNANCE_ONLY, VE_MODEL/FEE_SHARING/HIGH_STAKING_RATIO/BUYBACK_PROGRAM/LOW_REVENUE_CAPTURE flags, ring-buffer log, atomic writes) + MP-919 ProtocolSecurityIncidentTracker (109 tests, incident_rate_score/recency_risk/security_investment_score/composite_safety_score 0-100, VERY_SAFE..AVOID, RECENT_HACK/REPEAT_OFFENDER/NO_INSURANCE/UNAUDITED/RECOVERED_FUNDS flags, ring-buffer log, atomic writes). done_count 582->584, sprint_current v6.94->v6.97.",
  "_v700_dispatch_note": "SPA-V700: MP-924 DeFiPointsToTokenConversionAnalyzer (97 tests, implied_value_per_point_usd, implied_apy_pct, dilution_risk_score 0-100, comparison_premium_pct, EXCEPTIONAL..LIKELY_WORTHLESS labels, HIGH_DILUTION/DELAYED_AIRDROP/BETTER_THAN_PEERS/UNANNOUNCED_ALLOCATION/FARM_SATURATION flags, ring-buffer log 100, atomic writes) + MP-925 ProtocolFeeRevenueSustainabilityAnalyzer (101 tests, revenue_growth_rate_pct, revenue_per_tvl_pct, profit_margin_pct, revenue_quality_score/unit_economics_score 0-100, PROFITABLE..CRITICAL labels, GROWING_REVENUE/INCENTIVE_DEPENDENT/DECLINING_MARKET_SHARE/HIGH_PROFIT_MARGIN/NEGATIVE_MARGIN flags, ring-buffer log 100, atomic writes). 198 tests green. done_count 588->590, sprint_current v6.99->v7.00.",
  "_v701_dispatch_note": "SPA-V701: MP-926 DeFiVaultStrategyRiskDecomposer (107 tests, weighted sc/liquidity/oracle/counterparty risk, composite 0-100, CONSERVATIVE..SPECULATIVE labels, 4 flags, ring-buffer log, atomic writes) + MP-927 ProtocolCrossProtocolContagionAnalyzer (101 tests, dependency graph, in/out degree, contagion_risk_score/systemic_importance_score 0-100, ISOLATED..SYSTEMIC labels, circular dep detection DFS, 4 flags, ring-buffer log, atomic writes). 208 tests green. done_count 590->592, sprint_current v7.00->v7.01.",
  "_v702_dispatch_note": "SPA-V702: MP-928 DeFiYieldCurvePositionAnalyzer (fixed/variable rate positions, rate_advantage_pct, duration_risk_score, rate_risk_score, DV01, PnL ±100bps, RATE_ADVANTAGE/NEUTRAL/RATE_DISADVANTAGE/EXPIRING_SOON/UNDERWATER labels, HIGH_DURATION/INVERTED_ADVANTAGE/NEAR_EXPIRY/LARGE_DV01_EXPOSURE/BREAKEVEN_NEAR flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, ≥80 tests GREEN) + MP-929 ProtocolTokenomicsStressTester (price shock, post_shock_mcap, emission_sell_pressure, buyback_coverage_ratio, treasury_runway, staking_sustainability, viability_score 0-100, ANTIFRAGILE/RESILIENT/VULNERABLE/CRITICAL/TERMINAL labels, DEATH_SPIRAL_RISK/TREASURY_RUNWAY_SHORT/DEPENDENT_PROTOCOLS_AT_RISK/BUYBACK_COVERS flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, ≥85 tests GREEN). done_count 592->594, sprint_current v7.01->v7.02.",
  "_v704_dispatch_note": "SPA-V704: MP-932 DeFiPerpetualFundingRateAnalyzer (113 tests, funding cost/skew scoring, carry trade opportunity, 5 flags, ring-buffer log) + MP-933 ProtocolAirdropEligibilityOptimizer (99 tests, per-wallet×per-program eligibility scoring, 7 criteria types, 5 flags, completion roadmap). done_count 596->598, sprint_current v7.03->v7.04.",
