  "_v712_dispatch_note": "v7.12 self-authored code sprint: MP-948 DeFiLeverageLoopingOptimizer (83 tests) + MP-949 DeFiFixedRateDurationAnalyzer (81 tests) = 164 green. Backlog had only USER ACTION + P3 items, so two real-gap modules authored (no prior looping-leverage or fixed-rate/duration/convexity module). Reconcile note: KANBAN done column previously lagged at MP-933/v7.04 while push scripts v7.05-v7.11 (MP-934..947) already existed on disk; this run advanced sprint_completed to v7.12. Architect review skipped (v7.12 not multiple of 5; anthropic module unavailable in sandbox).",
