  "_v721_dispatch_note": "SPA-V721 self-authored code sprint: MP-966 DeFiStablecoinReserveQualityScorer (spa_core/analytics/defi_stablecoin_reserve_quality_scorer.py, 35 tests) + MP-967 DeFiLockupOpportunityCostAnalyzer (spa_core/analytics/defi_lockup_opportunity_cost_analyzer.py, 31 tests). Both advisory/read-only, pure stdlib, atomic writes, ring-buffer 100. Fill real gaps (no prior reserve/backing-quality module; no prior lockup opportunity-cost/hurdle module). Architect review attempted (v7.20 ends in 0) but anthropic module unavailable in sandbox -> manual backlog review: backlog held only USER ACTION (P0-P2) + P3 features/ideas.",
  "_v721_reconcile_note": "RECONCILE 2026-06-14: done-column lagged at MP-949/v7.12 while modules, tests and scripts/push_v713.sh..push_v720.sh (MP-950..MP-965, sprints v7.13-v7.20) were already shipped on disk and verified (202 tests green for v7.20). Backfilled done-column with MP-950..MP-965 plus new v7.21 MP-966/967. sprint_completed v7.12 -> v7.21; done_count -> 628. Added: MP-950, MP-951, MP-952, MP-953, MP-954, MP-955, MP-956, MP-957, MP-958, MP-959, MP-960, MP-961, MP-962, MP-963, MP-964, MP-965, MP-966, MP-967",
