  "_v744_dispatch_note": "SPA-V744: MP-1012 DeFiProtocolCrossAssetCorrelationRiskAnalyzer (99 tests, portfolio_volatility_pct/effective_diversification_ratio/herfindahl_concentration/chain_concentration_score/protocol_concentration_score/correlation_risk_score 0-100, 5 risk labels: WELL_DIVERSIFIED/ADEQUATELY_DIVERSIFIED/MODERATELY_CONCENTRATED/HIGHLY_CONCENTRATED/DANGEROUS_CONCENTRATION, 6 flags: ETH_CORRELATED_DOMINANCE/SINGLE_CHAIN_RISK/PROTOCOL_CONCENTRATION/STABLECOIN_BUFFER/EFFECTIVE_DIVERSIFICATION/EXTREME_CONCENTRATION, ring-buffer log cross_asset_correlation_log.json cap 100, atomic write) + MP-1013 ProtocolDeFiVetokenGovernancePowerAnalyzer (112 tests, lock_participation_ratio/vetoken_yield_pct/bribe_to_emission_ratio/governance_centralization_score/fee_to_bribe_ratio/lock_efficiency, 6 governance labels: HEALTHY_DEMOCRACY/FUNCTIONAL/PLUTOCRATIC_RISK/BRIBERY_DOMINATED/GOVERNANCE_CAPTURED/CLIFF_RISK, 6 flags: HIGH_PARTICIPATION/BRIBERY_ECONOMY/GOVERNANCE_ATTACK_HISTORY/CLIFF_EXPIRY_RISK/STRONG_FEE_BACKING/PLUTOCRATIC, ring-buffer log vetoken_governance_log.json cap 100, atomic write) — 211 tests GREEN, done_count 676->678, sprint_current v7.41->v7.44",
  "_v743_dispatch_note": "SPA-V743: MP-1010 DeFiProtocolLendingRateSpreadAnalyzer (92 tests, gross_spread_pct/effective_spread_pct/implied_protocol_revenue_pct/lender_yield_premium_pct/borrower_cost_premium_pct/spread_efficiency_score 0-100, 5 labels: TIGHT_SPREAD/EFFICIENT/NORMAL/WIDE_SPREAD/INEFFICIENT, 6 flags: HIGH_UTILIZATION_RISK/WIDE_SPREAD_OPPORTUNITY/LOW_RESERVE_FACTOR/PREMIUM_YIELD/LIQUIDATION_PROXIMITY/TIGHT_EFFICIENT_MARKET, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) + MP-1011 ProtocolDeFiYieldSourceSustainabilityRanker (103 tests, real_yield_pct/apy_stability_score/sustainability_score 0-100/risk_adjusted_yield/emission_dependency_risk, 6 labels: FORTRESS_YIELD/SUSTAINABLE/TRANSITIONAL/EMISSION_DEPENDENT/UNSUSTAINABLE/POINTS_SPECULATION, 6 flags: REAL_YIELD_DOMINANT/EMISSION_HEAVY/REVENUE_SURPLUS/AIRDROP_BOOSTED/COMPETITIVE_MOAT/YIELD_DECLINING, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) — 195 tests GREEN, done_count 678->680, sprint_current v7.41->v7.43",
  "_v745_dispatch_note": "SPA-V745: MP-1014 DeFiProtocolAdminKeyControlRiskAnalyzer (53 tests, multisig_strength/timelock/control_surface → admin_control_risk_score, FULLY_DECENTRALIZED..CRITICAL_CENTRALIZATION) + MP-1015 DeFiProtocolRehypothecationRiskAnalyzer (49 tests, geometric loop leverage / net carry / health buffer / liquidation drop / contagion → rehypothecation_risk_score). Также reconcile v7.41-v7.44 (MP-1006..1013 уже на диске, 805 tests verified). Self-authored — backlog без type=code/status=ready. Architect review пропущен (anthropic недоступен в sandbox). push_to_github.py НЕ запускался; создан scripts/push_v745.sh.",
  "_v745_reconcile_note": "v7.41-v7.44 push-скрипты (push_v741..744.sh, MP-1006..1013) уже были на диске; sprint_log.md и sprint_completed отставали на v7.40. Этот прогон поднял sprint_completed v7.40→v7.45, done_count 680→682, done-колонку дополнил MP-1006..1015.",
  "_v746_dispatch_note": "SPA-V746: MP-1016 DeFiProtocolNFTCollateralRiskAnalyzer (98 tests, liquidation_buffer/floor_drop_to_liquidation/liquidity_risk/oracle_risk/composite_nft_risk 0-100, NFT_FORTRESS/LOW_RISK/MODERATE_RISK/HIGH_RISK/LIQUIDATION_IMMINENT labels, NEAR_LIQUIDATION/FLOOR_PRICE_ORACLE/HIGH_LTV_NFT/BLUE_CHIP_PREMIUM/WASH_TRADING_SUSPECTED/LOW_LIQUIDITY_COLLECTION flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) + MP-1017 ProtocolDeFiRealWorldAssetBridgeAnalyzer (102 tests, redemption_risk/custody_risk/on_chain_transparency/yield_premium_over_tbill/overall_bridge_quality 0-100, INSTITUTIONAL_GRADE/HIGH_QUALITY/STANDARD/BELOW_STANDARD/HIGH_RISK_RWA labels, DAILY_REDEMPTION/UNREGULATED_CUSTODIAN/OPAQUE_REPORTING/YIELD_PREMIUM_POSITIVE/KYC_BARRIER/INSTITUTIONAL_ACCESSIBLE flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) — 200 tests GREEN, done_count 682->684, sprint_current v7.45->v7.46",
  "_v749_dispatch_note": "SPA-V749: MP-1022 DeFiProtocolSandwichAttackVulnerabilityScorer (113 tests, sandwich_profit_potential/front_run_cost_gwei/attack_feasibility_score/slippage_exposure/protection_score/net_vulnerability_score 0-100, PROTECTED/LOW_RISK/MODERATE_RISK/HIGH_RISK/SANDWICH_TARGET labels, MEMPOOL_EXPOSED/HIGH_SLIPPAGE_TOLERANCE/PROFITABLE_ATTACK/FLASHBOTS_SHIELDED/PRIVATE_RPC_USED/LARGE_TRADE_RISK flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) + MP-1023 ProtocolDeFiCrossChainYieldNormalizer (107 tests, total_bridge_cost/bridge_cost_annualized_pct/monthly_gas_cost/total_friction_pct/chain_risk_adjusted_apy/net_normalized_apy/position_viability_score, SUPERIOR_OPPORTUNITY/ATTRACTIVE/MARGINAL/FRICTION_DOMINATED/UNVIABLE labels, L2_NATIVE_ADVANTAGE/BRIDGE_HEAVY/GAS_INTENSIVE/POSITION_TOO_SMALL/HIGH_CHAIN_RISK/ETHEREUM_MAINNET_COST flags, chain_comparison per-chain avg net_apy, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) — 220 tests GREEN, done_count 688->690, sprint_current v7.48->v7.49",
  "_v750_reconcile_note": "v7.47 (MP-1018 LiquidityIncentiveEfficiencyScorer + MP-1019 PriceImpactDepthAnalyzer) и v7.48 (MP-1020 TokenUnlockImpactAnalyzer + MP-1021 StableYieldOptimizer) уже были на диске (модули+тесты+push_v747/748.sh), но отсутствовали в done-колонке, а sprint_completed отставал на v7.47. Этот прогон добавил MP-1018..1021 в done и поднял sprint_completed v7.47->v7.49. Все тесты v7.46-v7.49 (825) проверены в sandbox — green.",
  "_v750_dispatch_note": "SPA-V750: MP-1024 DeFiProtocolSequencerDowntimeRiskAnalyzer (94 tests, downtime_frequency_score/liquidation_exposure_score/escape_hatch_score/centralization_score -> net_downtime_risk_score 0-100, RESILIENT/LOW_RISK/MODERATE_RISK/HIGH_RISK/CRITICAL_EXPOSURE labels, SINGLE_SEQUENCER/NO_GRACE_PERIOD/NEAR_LIQUIDATION/NO_ESCAPE_HATCH/FREQUENT_DOWNTIME/LONG_MAX_OUTAGE/UPTIME_FEED_PROTECTED/FORCE_INCLUSION_AVAILABLE/DECENTRALIZATION_PLANNED/INSUFFICIENT_DATA flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) + MP-1025 ProtocolDeFiYieldDurationMismatchAnalyzer (90 tests, duration_gap_days/liquidity_coverage_ratio/redemption_stress_shortfall_pct/net_interest_margin_pct/duration_mismatch_score 0-100, MATCHED/MINOR_MISMATCH/MODERATE_MISMATCH/SEVERE_MISMATCH/RUN_RISK labels, 11 flags, ring-buffer log cap 100, atomic write) — 184 tests GREEN, done_count 690->692, sprint_completed v7.49->v7.50. Self-authored код-спринт (backlog: только USER ACTION P0-P2 + P3 features/ideas, готовых type=code/status=ready нет). Gap-check grep'ом по 455 analytics-модулям: sequencer/downtime/censorship=0, duration_mismatch/asset_liability=0. Architect review (v7.50 кратен 5): spa_core.dev_agents.architect/anthropic недоступен в sandbox -> ручной backlog-review. Push: scripts/push_v750.sh (ручной запуск на Mac, PAT fallback Keychain->GITHUB_PAT_SPA->SPA_GITHUB_PAT->~/.github_pat, без hardcoded секретов).",
  "_v751_dispatch_note": "SPA-V751: MP-1026 DeFiProtocolGovernanceProposalImpactScorer (107 tests) + MP-1027 ProtocolDeFiProtocolRevenueSustainabilityAnalyzer (109 tests) — 216 tests GREEN, done_count 690->692, sprint_current v7.50->v7.51",
