  "_v818_dispatch_note": "v8.18 self-authored code sprint: MP-1154 DepositCapHeadroom + MP-1155 DepositorConcentration (123+117=240 tests). Backlog had no type=code/status=ready tasks (only USER ACTION P0-P2 + P3 features + LOW ideas). Closes gaps deposit_cap=0, depositor_concentration=0. Registry Tier-B +2 (new category vault_capacity). Last completed v8.17 not multiple of 5 -> no architect review. push_v818.sh created for manual run on Mac.",
  "_v819_dispatch_note": "v8.19 self-authored код-спринт (нет ready type=code в backlog; в backlog только USER ACTION P0-P2 MP-017/UA-004/UA-006/MP-313/MP-379 и AGENT-P0/P1-* type=agent_infra, требующие git/launchd/keychain на Mac — недоступно из sandbox). Созданы 2 advisory/read-only анализатора: MP-1156 ShareInflationAttackExposure (cat vault_safety) и MP-1157 VaultIdleCashDrag (cat capital_efficiency). 137+129=266 тестов зелёные. Push: scripts/push_v819.sh (ручной запуск на Mac).",
  "_v820_dispatch_note": "v8.20 self-authored код-спринт (нет ready type=code в backlog; только USER ACTION P0-P2 MP-017/UA-004/UA-006/MP-313/MP-379 и AGENT-P0/P1-* type=agent_infra, требующие git/launchd/keychain на Mac — недоступно из sandbox). Созданы 2 advisory/read-only анализатора: MP-1158 VaultPendingHarvestPremium (cat vault_timing) и MP-1159 VaultRoundTripCost (cat cost_efficiency). 132+134=266 тестов green. Pure stdlib, атомарный ring-buffer, registry Tier-B +2. Architect review не требуется (v8.19 не кратен 5). Push: scripts/push_v820.sh (ручной запуск на Mac). Верифицировано независимо оркестратором: py_compile OK, unittest Ran 266 OK, forbidden-import grep CLEAN, data-стабы [], нет .tmp.",
  "_v824_dispatch_note": "v8.24 self-authored код-спринт: MP-1166 VaultCapacityDilutionAnalyzer (yield_quality) + MP-1167 VaultHarvestTimingAnalyzer (cost_efficiency); 168+164=332 tests green; registry Tier-B 414→416; gaps подтверждены грепом (capacity_dilution=0, harvest_timing=0). push_to_github.py НЕ запускался (sandbox) — создан scripts/push_v824.sh для ручного запуска на Mac.",
  "_v826_dispatch_note": "v8.26 self-authored: MP-1170 RewardTokenPriceExposure (yield_quality) + MP-1171 MaturityTrackRecord (protocol_health). 168+174=342 tests green. registry Tier-B 420->422 (total 614). No ready type=code tasks in backlog (only USER ACTION P0-P2 + agent_infra needing Mac/git/keychain). Architect review: v8.25 multiple of 5 -> trigger, but spa_core.dev_agents.architect unavailable in sandbox (anthropic/api.github.com/Keychain) -> manual gap/backlog grep-review done. push_to_github.py NOT run; scripts/push_v826.sh created for manual Mac run."
